section(id="features" class="feature_section gradiant padding-top-80 padding-bottom-80")
  div(class="container")
    div(class="section_heading mb-40 align-center")
      amp-img(class="lazy section_icon" alt="features" src="/img/shape_46x44@2x.png" width="46px" height="44px")
      h2 Features
    div(class="row feature_wrap")
      div(class="col-md-5")
        ul(class="feature_content feature_left align-right")
          li(class="wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay="0ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Spaced Repetition Scheduling
            p This is a famous scheduling algorithm to help you memorize vocabulary better.
          li(class="wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay="0ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Memorize by Writing 
            p This helps you effectively memorize terms by actively writing them along with spaced repetition scheduling.
          li(class="wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay="150ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Mini Games
            p It includes mini-games for you to practice and brush up terms you have learned.
          li(class="wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay="300ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Built-in Dictionaries
            p It comes with built-in dictionaries for you to make flashcards easier.
          li(class="wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay="300ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Built-in Translation
            p You can also use Google Translate to translate terms in realtime for references.
          li(class="wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay="300ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Extra Fields Support
            p You can add additional information associated with the terms, such as IPA, synonym and so on.
          li(class="wow fadeInRight" data-wow-delay="300ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Unlimited Sets & Flashcards
            p There are no limitations on the number of sets and vocabulary you can add.
      div(class="col-md-2")
      div(class="col-md-5")
        ul(class="feature_content feature_right align-left")
          li(class="wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay="300ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Sync with Google Sheets
            p We developed Google Sheets add-on for you to import and export terms with ease. 
          li(class="wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay="300ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Bulk Action
            p You can select multiple terms or categories then perform actions on them at once.
          li(class="wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay="300ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Discovery
            p We make it easy for you to discover essential and new terms to learn.
          li(class="wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay="0ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Auto Syncing
            p The app automatically backups and synchronizes changes with our remote servers.
          li(class="wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay="150ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Auto Archive
            p You can set up rules to automatically archive terms that you have learned.
          li(class="wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay="300ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Smart Searching
            p You can search added terms by whole words, by definitions, or by prefixes.
          li(class="wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-delay="300ms" data-wow-duration="1000ms")
            h3 Offline Access
            p While offline, you can still perform some actions, such as adding or editing terms.
